  <steps>
    <step num="0">In a mug, whisk together flour, sugar, baking powder, and kosher salt. </step>
    <step num="1">Add milk, butter, and vanilla. Mix until smooth. </step>
    <step num="2">Stir in lemon zest and blueberries. </step>
    <step num="3">Microwave for 1½-2 minutes, or until cake appears puffy and cooked through. </step>
    <step num="4">Cool 2 minutes. Top with sparkling sugar (optional). </step>
    <step num="5">Enjoy! </step>
  </steps>
